snippet.title: クック・ドゥ・ドゥル・ドゥー (RPGツクールSUPER DANTE) | Cock-A-Doodle-Doo (BS) (Satellaview)
snippet.description:
Well, whadaya know! Cock-A-Doodle-Doo was on the Satellaview!

Because of the differences between Super Dante and Dante98, the experiences are pretty different between the versions of "Cock-A-Doodle-Doo". Here's some gameplay of it on the Super Famicom!

Compare and contrast with the Dante98 version with the help of this video!
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DsdR7_-q6rs

The Satellaview/Super Dante version will be released soon on Satellablog!
http://superfamicom.org/blog/
